Brian Murphy (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Murphy_(actor) 0 Brian Trevor John Murphy (born 25 September 1932) is an English actor and comedian, best known as the henpecked husband George Roper in the popular sitcom Man About the House and its spin-off series George and Mildred, and as Alvin Smedley in Last of the Summer Wine.
